Amazing store and people.

My first impression walking into the store was wow they really care and love all the reptiles, arachnids, and amphibians that they have within the store. The enclosures they are kept in are beautiful and well looked after aswell as the store itself. I am really happy I was able to get my first 2 pet frogs (Froakie and Loki) from this store.

They answered all my questions and took the time to help me understand everything they were saying so I could provide the best and correct care for my frogs. They also took the time to help me set up my tank with my drainage layer, tree wood and vine leaves, the frogs were secured perfeclty making the jouney home less of an anxious time.

Both frogs have settled in well and whenever I go in to buy food they always ask how I'm getting on as well as how both frogs are doing and if they are moving around, eating well, etc. Overall both husband and wife are extremely lovely people and i am very grateful I was able to use the store to get my frogs and equipment.
